title: Portable Photoshop CS6 Extended 13.0.1 Multilingual
description:
Portable Photoshop CS6 Extended 13.0.1 Multilingual

Portable Photoshop CS6 13.0.1 Extended Multilingual | Win | 93.5 MB


Graphic editor without installation (English, Czech, Danish, German, Spanish, SpanishInternational, Finnish, French, Hungarian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Norwegian, Dutch, Polish, PortugueseBR, Romanian, Russian, Swedish, Turkish, Ukrainian, SimpChinese, TradChinese).

Language set by launcher according UserDefaultLang.
To change, edit PhotoshopCS6Portable.ini with Language="one of the extensions of tw10428 in AppPhotoshopCS6Localesen_AESupport Files".
You can add plug-ins in AppPhotoshopCS6Plug-ins.

Run PhotoshopCS6Portable.
Don't run at the same time of another Adobe product or if you have Photoshop installed!
